	<h1 id="rest-item itemshippingprofiles">
		REST Item ItemShippingProfiles
	</h1>

	<p>Activate, deactivate or list shipping profiles linked to an item.<br />Shipping profiles are used to centrally manage the different types of delivery offered for the store's product portfolio. Shipping profiles are created and managed centrally and then activated on the item level. By activating a shipping profile for an item, specific shipping information, e.g. shipping costs and the shipping provider to be used, are linked to the specific item. All items should be linked to at least one shipping profile to ensure that shipping costs are calculated correctly. If an order contains items for which no shipping profile is activated, the items will be assigned the default shipping profile of the default online store. If no default shipping profile exists, the shipping profile with the highest priority will be used.<br />Shipping profiles are managed using the route /rest/orders/shipping/presets.</p>

